{"tid":314467,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★張建宗稱教育是促進向上流最有效方法！！","createTime":"2017-07-09T08:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T12:00:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae20ec634432c0f0ba56d6a146480c1a3ffd2434","tid":314467,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T08:53:54.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗在網誌表示，新一屆問責團隊全速投入工作，認為教育是培育人才、促進年輕人向上流動的最有效方法。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗表示，投資教育就是投資香港未來，行政長官林鄭月娥已率先公布增加50億元經常教育開支，新措施將有助穩定教學人員的工作環境，吸引年輕教師及專業人才投身教育界，創造有前景的就業機會，提升教學質素。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗提到，政府會為青年人創造更多向上流動的機會，包括推出多項內地和海外交流、工作假期、在職培訓等；政府亦正為約50名大學生提供暑期實習生計劃，從中多關心、聆聽年輕人的心聲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1340975-20170709.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1340975-20170709.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Gfdbwq9nmw8goxw5dM3r3MmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=7a594ff2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1340975-20170709.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e202af0b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1340975-20170709.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1340975_1_20170709104038.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1340975_1_20170709104038.jpg&h=a48531d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"596240f511f9db6abb70e5cc343ebab3e1532f74","tid":314467,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T08:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3c4871bd8781772e703ac23f87e45fc67d4881","tid":314467,"uid":67298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T08:56:07.000Z","msg":"50名皇恩浩蕩"},{"pid":"b63050a502e286b6905ae7123bbb884822a9a1e1","tid":314467,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017